$Revision: 530668 $ $Date: 2007-04-20 01:40:54 -0500 (Fri, 20 Apr 2007) $ The "attribute" element represents a named, typed, value associated with the parent UIComponent via the generic attributes mechanism. Attribute names must be unique within the scope of the parent (or related) component.
